The paper discusses a novel test-bed platform for reinforcement learning research from raw visual information, specifically in a first-person perspective in a semi-realistic 3D world. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision (cs.CV), Graphics (cs.GR), and Robotics (cs.RO).
